      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-esp-cli-esp    =    zero or
                     w-det-esp-cli-wac    =    zero
                     go to rou-det-cec-900.
      *
           if        w-det-esp-cli-esp    >    w-det-esp-cli-wac
                     move  "#"            to   w-det-esp-cli-olf      .
       rou-det-cec-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
