                                          into w-vis-rif-ocl-x40
                                  with pointer w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riposizionamento puntatore              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt      .
           inspect   w-vis-rif-ocl-x40
                                      tallying w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt
                                          for  trailing spaces        .
           subtract  w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt    from 40
                                        giving w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt      .
           add       2                    to   w-vis-rif-ocl-pnt      .
       vis-rif-ocl-020.
