           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      65                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-err-box-err-msg    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
